{
  "stem": "26699.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People weren't allowed to move anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were rules and authorities, which were totally anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wouldn't let anybody move from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were stuck to your place and report to the local authorities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In [PAUSES] June next year, [PAUSES] [CLEARS THROAT] as the Germans started to implement their Final Solution, the Romanians, [CLEARS THROAT] some people say under pressure, some of them, they say voluntarily, started to have a census of the Jewish population, what they called population of Jewish blood.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not of Jewish [CLEARS THROAT] religion, of Jewish blood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because there were possible people who converted to Christianity or had only half of their parents of Jewish origin [PAUSES] who could have passed as Christians.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was specific in their law that anybody who has Jewish blood needs to be registered as such.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now it was a big dilemma for my parents when they receive the forms to fill in, if to register me there or not, or to keep me in hiding.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Eventually, [PAUSES] all of us, we were registered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I kept this certificate of my [PAUSES] Jewish affiliation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Probably the intention was if things were going well with the German conquest of Russia, to finish us off in one of the extermination camps.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But things went differently.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had a relative quiet life in Iasi after the pogrom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could go to school, albeit it was a bad location.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the school was good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The teachers were good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We could go occasionally to a restaurant to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So more or less, the life was quasi-normal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What was the attitude of the general population to Jews?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't say that it was [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] [CLEARS THROAT] too vicious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They weren't friendly with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them, they were legionnaires.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
